(130, '2019-09-03', 'International', 'Australia tour packages', 'Australia_1_555x555.jpg', 'Australia.jpg', '7', 'Tourism in Australia is an important component of the Australian economy. Popular Australian destinations include the coastal cities of Sydney, Brisbane, and Melbourne ,etc.            ', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Australia Tour Package</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">A haven for adventure enthusiasts travel junkies and serenity seekers, Australia is famous for a number of reasons. A trip to Australia comes with bundle experiences which are to be cherished forever. Besides admiring scenic beauty one can enjoy thrilling adventures, amazing train journeys and savouring world-class cuisines.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Choose from a wide range of Australia tour packages and get ready for a memorable sojourn. Go through a variety of itineraries which appeal to almost all travellers with their personal needs and preferences. Although small yet Australia is the most sought-after holiday destination in the world. Take a tour to experience what surprises the country has in store for you.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">During your Australia holidays, you get to witness a perfect m&eacute;lange of exotic wildlife, beguiling scenery, stunning attractions and so on. Add to it, partaking in adventure sports and exploring diving destinations to make your trip memorable. Hailed as the &lsquo;Land of Kangaroos&rsquo;, the amazing country lures beach lovers, nature enthusiasts and party freaks from worldwide.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Our experts put in lots of efforts to make your Australia travel convenient. With years of experience, they suggest the best packages for you. Whether you are a couple, travelling with your family or looking for a solo offbeat vacation, we&rsquo;re happy to help. Be it a long trip or short, an active holiday or a relaxing stay or whatever your travel style may be; we can plan everything easily.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Plan an Australia tour and you will be enchanted by its impressive diversity, urging you to spend a lifetime here. Cherishing Australia&#39;s coastal and aquatic experiences, distinctive nature, wine and food are some of the major highlights of your sojourn. Partaking in a plethora of marine and fun activities is an added plus and raises the fun quotient to the next level.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Sparkling skyscrapers, sunny climate, numerous theme parks, vibrant nightlife and thriving, subtropical hinterland of the rainforest make it ideal for honeymooners. Also, the attractive and lively vibe of Gold Coast, make it feature in the Australia honeymoon packages. A tour to this spectacular destination is all about exploring pristine beaches, spectacular rainforest and natural beauty ranging from Outback to Uluru.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tibet Tour Packages&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tibet, the highest region on earth, is extremely well-known for its culture and traditions. A large number of tourists from all around the world visit Tibet every year to explore its natural beauty, major attractions, religious sites and much more. Famed as &lsquo;Roof of the World&rsquo; and the &lsquo;Third Pole of the Earth&rsquo;, it can be perfectly discovered by opting for Tours to Tibet by Indian Holiday.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">During your visit to Tibet, you must explore some extremely mesmerizing destinations like Lhasa, Xigatse and Gyantse. Home to Tibetans, Tibet also is the homeland of some ethnic groups like Monpas, Lhobas and Qiang. While on a visit, you must not miss visiting prime tourist attractions like the Potala Palace, Jokhang temple, Namtaso Lake, Mount Kailash and Qomolangma National Nature Reserve.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_1'),
(131, '2019-09-03', 'International', 'Bhutan  tour packages', 'Bhutan_555x555.jpg', 'bhutan.jpg', '7', 'The very words give us glimpses of a remote land replete with monks, monasteries, yaks, Buddhist art and much more. Bhutan is no longer so remote and features as a must-see destination.            ', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bhutan Tour Packages</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Tucked in the lap of the Himalayas, Bhutan is one of the last remaining Kingdoms. The Shangri-La is set amid the world&rsquo;s most beautiful mountain range. It is blessed with ethereal views, vibrant culture, trekking opportunities and what can only be described as the best time of your life. With Bhutan tour packages, discover the bliss of the last paradise on Earth. Home to snow-draped peaks, lush valleys, ancient monasteries, incredible architecture, colorful culture, happy people and experiences that bring a smile to your face.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">When the measure is happiness, Bhutan is among the happiest places in the world. This fact reveals how prosperous the country is and how well they treat their guests. Every moment of a Bhutan holiday is made special as is every experience worth cherishing. If its mystery you seek, then the country is shrouded in many fables of the old. If you would love to escape the crowds then there are so many of the unexplored pristine spots that you would definitely lose count. And what can one say about the plethora of places to visit and things to do, each one is an important aspect of Bhutan tour.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The Buddhist nation is known for the colorful prayer flags fluttering in the air, prayer wheels and scenic monasteries. The grand examples of traditional design and architecture, they have much to offer to enthrall visitors. The iconic Tiger&rsquo;s Nest is an out-of-the world lying precariously over sheer cliff tops. Many of the known and the explored monasteries stand as majestic guards over pictorial towns. Buddhist culture is also unmissable part of Bhutan packages. Their traditions add to the beautiful experiences the country has to offer. Masked dances, songs, dances, plays, dramatization, and other stage efficiencies make the culture endearing.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Choose Bhutan travel packages that cover major tourist attractions like Tiger&rsquo;s Nest Monastery, Punakha Dzong, or Pungtang Dechen Phodrang (Palace of Great Happiness), Taktsang Monastery, Phobjikha and Gangtey Valley, National Folk Heritage Museum, Trashi Chhoe Dzong, etc. Excursion to National Memorial Stupa, Textile Museum, the Changangkha Temple, etc. are also a must.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">The heavenly food, mixture of Indian, Chinese, Tibetan delicacies is what makes Bhutan holidays all the more special. The charming hotels with the most lavish amenities only enhance the thrill. While with family you can creates the most beautiful memories, Bhutan honeymoon packages is an absolute stunner. What better than to begin a new life in the heavenly bliss.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Choose any of the Bhutan holiday packages and cherish memories of a lifetime. The traffic light free country does not know to stop the traffic of excitements. The mesmerizing country welcomes all kinds of travelers equally. Be it your get away from your schedules, family vacation, romantic honeymoon, adventure or juts finding your happiness, browse through our well-crafted Bhutan tours from India.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_3', 'Sinda_tours_travels_3'),
(132, '2019-09-03', 'International', 'Azerbaijan tour packages', 'Azerbaijan_555x555.jpg', 'Azerbaijan Tour Packages.jpg', '7', 'Beautiful nature, characterized by a diverse landscape, magnificent architecture, rich cultural heritage as well as the overall development of the country present lots of opportunities for pastime.             ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Azerbaijan Tour Packages</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Showcasing a perfect confluence of the east and the west, Azerbaijan is replete with a number of attractions. It is because of these charms, that the Azerbaijan tour packages from India remain in huge demand. Often known as the &lsquo;Land of Fire&rsquo;, the country never fails to amuse the visitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Be it the Fire Mountain, Mud Volcanoes, seaside resorts or ancient mosques, everything seems to cast a spell on the tourists. Home to astounding architectures, engaging cities, National Parks and majestic sea, Azerbaijan is nothing less than a dreamland.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Plan a trip to Azerbaijan and escape into mountain or beaches, the country has something to offer to everybody. Flaunting two UNESCO World Heritage Sites, the intriguing destination enjoys a rich history. Azerbaijan is an ideal place to cherish several experiences under a single roof.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_2', 'Sinda_tours_travels_2'),
(133, '2019-09-03', 'International', 'Cambodia tour packages', 'Cambodia_555x555.jpg', 'Cambodia tour packages.jpg', '7', 'Cambodia is famous for a Hindu temple known as Angkor Wat temple. Here the sunrise is the most captivate thing.                         ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><strong>Cambodia Tour Packages</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Cambodia is one of the most fascinating Southeast Asian destinations, which can best be explored by opting for Cambodia tour packages, designed by us in a meticulous manner. The place has gems like rich history and culture, busy cities, traditional villages, thick jungles and ancient Khmer temples. During your Cambodia tours, do not miss visiting Angor Wat, the biggest Hindu temple complex. The site of River Mekong flowing towards Tonle Sap Lake is a memorable one and must be visited.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Cambodia holiday packages are incomplete without a visit to the pristine Sihanoukville beach. Other attractions include capital city Phnom Penh, Kirirom, Rattanakiri, and Kampot. Baypn and the ruins of Khmer empire are unmissable too.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_4', 'Sinda_tours_travels_4'),
(134, '2019-09-03', 'International', 'Nepal  tour packages', 'Nepal.jpg', 'Nepal.jpg', '7', 'According to , major tourist activities include wilderness and adventure activities such as mountain biking, bungee jumping, rock climbing, and mountain climbing ,etc.                                    ', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>Best Nepal Tour Packages</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Nestled amidst the mighty Himalayas, Nepal is known for its rich culture, traditions and some of the highest mountain peaks in the world that includes Mt. Everest. If in any case, you are thinking of bowled over by the stunning snow-laden mountains, then you must visit Nepal right now. From monasteries, temples, wildlife, stupas, enchanting places to anything and everything that you can imagine, the country has it all.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">With our collection of the best Nepal tour packages, you can go to the amazing tourist spots in the country to get the feel of scenic beauty, local culture, traditions and idyllic atmosphere to the fullest. Getting deep insights into the exquisite culture of the place is an eye-opening experience and can be better cherished with a well-planned tour package like the ones offered by us.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">The rugged terrain of Nepal has also paved path for various types of adventure tours. One can embark on a number of adventure trips such as mountain hiking, Nepal trekking, mountain cycling, mountain biking and other sports to give you that much-cherished adrenaline rush. You can go for adventure tours to places such as Annapurna base camp, Everest base camp and so on.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Our collection of Nepal travel packages from Delhi as well as Kathmandu and elsewhere will take you to some of the most sacred temples, mighty Himalayan peaks and UNESCO inscribed World Heritage Sites. With us by your side, you can rest assured that your Nepal Trip will be the one you will love to cherish forever.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Take a break from the hectic schedule and plan your Nepal Bhutan tour right now! This tour is designed based on your tastes and preferences. Offering much more than just normal sightseeing, the tour allows you delight in some memorable experiences.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">The Nepal Bhutan Tibet tour further allows you to get a glimpse into the rich culture and heritage. No doubt, Nepal as well as the Himalayan region in Bhutan, Tibet and North East India present a sight to behold. Besides, the tour also gives you a chance to treat your taste buds to some sizzling momos and other Tibetan delicacies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_6', 'Sinda_tours_travels_6'),
