(137, '2019-09-03', 'International', 'Seychelles tour packages', 'Seychelles_holidays_1_555x555.jpg', 'Seychelles tour packages.jpg', '7', 'Seychelles is a paradise on Earth. The beautiful country is blessed with deep blue waters and white sandy beaches with exotic sea life, becoming a famous honeymoon destination.            ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Seychelles Tour Packages</strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Roll the dice out and Seychelles will give enough reasons to go smile about. To come to think of it, Seychelles doesn&rsquo;t dominate over the Indian Ocean, spin around the globe and you would know. But as you pack your bags for a trip to this island nation off the coast of East Africa, you might just stumble. What surprised you more, the 115 islands here or their overwhelming charm? We know it&rsquo;s hard to decide, so why don&rsquo;t you take a Seychelles trip and do all the thinking en-route.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">This one destination is perfect for innumerable kinds of travelers. Couples who love being surrounded by serenity and tranquility, opt for this island nation without second thoughts. For them, we also have Seychelles honeymoon packages that bring the fairytale bliss to their love get away.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">There is no doubt on the fact that Seychelles is just as perfect for solo travelers and people flying with friends and family. The color changing sky, powdery sand, and aquamarine waters are the everyday scene you will love no matter where you go on this island nation.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Our Seychelles holidays also take the curious minds to meet the wild giant tortoises that find their refuge only in a few places in the world. Among other things on the itinerary, you also get to visit Aldabra, the second largest coral atoll in the world and a UNESCO World Heritage Site.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Further, Mah&eacute;, La Digue, and Praslin are the three main islands worth visiting. Mah&eacute; is your passage to the world of sand and sea, you have to hire a cycle in La Digue to explore all the unspoiled beaches. Along with that, this destination is known for serving your growling stomach with delectable delicacies.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">When it comes to Praslin, make sure you have a lot of time in hand to spend here. This island is best known for snorkeling, a visit to the offbeat Praslin Waterfall is also an experience like no other. Moreover, your Seychelles vacation is not complete if you don&rsquo;t visit the Vall&eacute;e de Mai Nature Reserve, a UNESCO World Heritage Site housing Coco de Mer palm and the endangered black parrot. You can find a number of hotels and resorts along with prismatic beaches. The best way to capture all the experiences in Praslin is by hiring a car.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">For a memorable trip, browse through our Seychelles tour packages. Our travel experts make sure that not a single thing goes missing in your itinerary and if so happens, you can </span></span></p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_tours_travels_7', 'Sinda_tours_travels_7'),
(140, '2019-09-03', 'India', 'Madhya Pradesh Tours Packages', 'Madhya_Pradesh__555x555.jpg', 'Madhya Pradesh.jpg', '7', 'Popularly known as the heart of India, Madhya Pradesh is famous for its natural beauty and cultural heritage. The rich and exotic flora & fauna, historical monuments, fort & palaces.... ', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt\">Madhya Pradesh Tour Packages</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Popularly known as the heart of India, Madhya Pradesh is famous for its natural beauty and cultural heritage. The rich and exotic flora &amp; fauna, historical monuments, fort &amp; palaces, high mountain ranges, thick green forests, and diverse culture of Madhya Pradesh allure tourists from all over the world. Madhya Pradesh was ruled by a number of rulers from different dynasties. Because of the rule of different rulers, today, Madhya Pradesh offers every visitor with different tourist attractions which feature different forms of architectural styles.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Madhya Pradesh is most popularly known for housing the famous Kanha National Park and Bandhavgarh National Park which is known for its rich flora and fauna. Also, the state is famous for the Khajuraho Group of Monuments which has been declared as World Heritage Sites by UNESCO. Sanchi and Bhimbetka are other famous attractions of Madhya Pradesh which have been declared as World Heritage Sites by UNESCO. Other popular attractions of the state include Gwalior, Ujjain, Bhopal, Pachmarhi, Orchha and Jabalpur. The star attraction of Madhya Pradesh is the wide variety of cuisines it offers. Popular cuisines offered in the state include Rajasthani and Gujarati cuisines.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">There is a lot to explore in this incredible state of India. Pack up your bags and get ready to enjoy a holidays in Madhya Pradesh with Madhya Pradesh Tour Packages from Indian Holiday. There is a lot to explore in this incredible state of India. Pack up your bags and get ready to enjoy a unique traveling experience in the colorful state of Madhya Pradesh with Madhya Pradesh Tour Packages from Indian Holiday.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Madhya _Pradesh', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Madhya _Pradesh'),
(141, '2019-09-03', 'India', 'Rajasthan Tour Packages', 'rajasthan_555x555.jpg', 'Rajasthan.jpg', '7', 'Given a chance to time travel and relish the magical expanse of Royal Rajasthan, you wouldn’t stop yourself from living each moment twice.....', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Rajasthan Tour Packages&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Given a chance to time travel and relish the magical expanse of Royal Rajasthan, you wouldn&rsquo;t stop yourself from living each moment twice. After all, it is not just a state, it is the pride of its bygone rulers and the joy in the voice of people who say &lsquo;Padharo Mhare Desh&rsquo;. The desire to catch the floating bubbles of culture, traditions, history and its royalty never ends, but travelers can at least start from somewhere with our Rajasthan tour Packages.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#4f81bd\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Why is Rajasthan famous for its tourism?</span></strong></strong></span></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">One destination, innumerable attractions! Tourists from all over the world find the royal state of Rajasthan a prime tourist destination in India. Owing to a number of vibrant cities Jodhpur and Jaipur, traditional puppet show, its folk dance &amp; music, palaces and forts, golden Desert, delectable food, colorful festivals, Shopping etc., Rajasthan cast a spell.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Traditional puppet show &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>Nowhere else you&rsquo;ll get to witness and listen to the stories of the Kings and Queens in such an entertaining way! Decorated puppets dancing to the traditional tunes and narrating amazing incidents present a sight to behold. Only Rajasthanis can keep alive the old-age tradition of puppet-show with such grace.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Folk Dance &amp; Music &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>It is the folk dance and music of the Rajasthan that urges you to tap your foot and match some steps with the locals. The magic of traditional instruments like pungi or been will make you leave all your worries behind.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Forts and palaces -</strong>&nbsp;The very name of Rajasthan conjures up the image of hilltop fortresses, maharajas with scimitars riding the painted elephants, the exquisitely carved havelis and the royal hunting grounds.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Golden Desert &ndash;&nbsp;</strong>The soft smooth silky golden sand covering a vast stretch tickles you when it slips under your feet. Appearing to be glittering liquid gold, the desert is the pride of Rajasthan and a perfect place to spend the night under the star-laden sky.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Delectable Food &ndash;</strong>&nbsp;Rajasthani cuisines are surely a treat to your taste buds and make this Rajawadi land of Rajputs a paradise for foodies.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">In fact, we&#39;re here to Rajasthan travel guide, Our Rajasthan holiday packages are designed to offer you a peek into the era where all you get to relish are opulence and artistry. These small things counted together make Rajasthan one of the most popular tourist places in India.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Rajasthan', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Rajasthan'),
(142, '2019-09-03', 'India', 'Goa Tours packages', 'Goa.jpg', 'Goa.jpg', '7', 'Our fine collection of Goa tour packages help you cherish memorable holidays in Goa amidst the swaying palms, white sands & sparkling waters. Savor delicious cuisines, enjoy the vibrant nightlife....            ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><strong>Goa Holiday Packages</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Our fine collection of Goa tour packages help you cherish memorable holidays in Goa amidst the swaying palms, white sands &amp; sparkling waters. Savor delicious cuisines, enjoy the vibrant nightlife and just let go of yourself with the characteristic susegad vibe. Practice yoga and meditation or rejuvenate yourself with therapeutic spa sessions at one of the fine luxury hotels in Goa. Our meticulously designed Goa holiday packages include all these and much more.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Goa also happens to be one of the most popular places to go for honeymoon in India. With this mind, we present the best <strong>Goa honeymoon tour packages</strong>. These packages help you curate memories of a lifetime by cherishing unmatched experiences. Stroll on the soft sand while holding each other&rsquo;s hand. Marvel at the spectacular sunset views and transform your evening into a magical affair.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">We not only cater to the needs of the newly wedded couples but also have a lot in store for avid travelers. Our <strong>Goa family tour packages</strong> allow you to experience the beauty of sparkling beaches and delight in a lush countryside ambiance. Reckoned as one of the finest beach destinations in India, the &lsquo;Party Capital&rsquo; lures holidaymakers from every nook and corner. The best time to visit Goa is from October till March. However, one should not miss planning <strong>North and South Goa tour</strong> in December and February to participate in various festivals.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Choose from any of the Goa travel package&nbsp;offered by IHPL and you will be transferred to the land of sand, sun and beaches. Boasting of a potpourri of colonial wonders, architecture, beaches, and the majestic forts, Goa promises to leave you spellbound. Trying your hands on the various adventure activities including water sports is one of the best things to do in Goa.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Goa&rsquo;s unique culture and lifestyle will urge you to plan a trip again and again. To help you with that, we have&nbsp;holiday trip to Goa. Crafted specially for you, these packages include everything that you are going to love about the lively state.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Goa', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Goa'),
(143, '2019-09-03', 'India', 'Agra Tours Package', 'Agra.jpg', 'Agra.jpg', '7', 'Agra has become almost synonymous with the legendary Taj Mahal. Several travel packages are offered to the tourists to make their vacation a delightful experience....', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><strong>Holiday Packages in Agra&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Agra has become almost synonymous with the legendary Taj Mahal. Several travel packages are offered to the tourists to make their vacation a delightful experience.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">To make the tour a memorable one, choose form the various tour packages like honeymoon tour package, fort and palaces tour package, wildlife tours, golden triangle tours, heritage and cultural tours and city sightseeing tours.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Agra', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Agra'),
(144, '2019-09-03', 'India', 'Himachal Pradesh Tour package ', 'shimla-manali-honeymoon.jpg', 'Himachal Pradesh.jpg', '7', 'If your idea of holiday in India is being footloose with Himalayas and communion with nature, nothing beats Himachal Pradesh literally meaning “the land in the lap of Himalayas”. ...                                    ', '<h1 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt\"><strong>Himachal Pradesh Tour Packages</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">If your idea of holiday in India is being footloose with Himalayas and communion with nature, nothing beats Himachal Pradesh literally meaning &ldquo;the land in the lap of Himalayas&rdquo;. With Himachal Tour Packages<strong>, </strong>explore picturesque hill stations, gushing waterfalls, abundant wildlife, emerald lakes, Trans Himalayan treks, snowcapped mountains and the barren beauty of upper Himalayas.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Our collection of Himachal Pradesh Holiday Packages is ideally suited for diverse themes when it comes to planning your holidays in India. Choose any of the Himachal tour packages for couple and cherish your honeymoon in India at Shimla, Dalhousie and Manali. Endowed with natural beauty, these popular hill stations are a must add-ons in any of the <strong>honeymoon packages</strong>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">For adventure tours in Himachal Pradesh, take your pick from best Himachal Tour Packages featuring destinations in Lahaul and Spiti Valley. There are several high altitude lakes, thrilling trekking routes and snowcapped mountain to be explored. You can also go paragliding in Bir Billing by choosing from our collection of<strong> </strong>Himachal Pradesh Tour Packages from Delhi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Not only from Delhi, but Himachal tour packages from Mumbai are also highly preferred because of the number of charms the state offers. Whether traveling solo, with family or with friends Himachal welcomes all kinds of travelers. This is also the reason that Himachal tour packages from Ahmedabad remain in huge demand.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Replete with temples, hill stations, lakes and snowcapped mountains, vacations in Himachal Pradesh are ideally suited for family summer holidays in India, honeymoon tour, <strong>adventure of trekking</strong>, road trips, motorcycle tours and heritage holiday.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;</p>\r\n', '1', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Himachal', 'Sinda_Tours_Travels_Himachal');

